      "topic": "html",
      "sender": "Engineer",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>商品详情页</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --color-red: #D62828;\n            --color-orange: #F77F00;\n            --color-light: #F4F4F5;\n            --color-dark: #003049;\n            --color-primary: #F77F00;\n        }\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--color-light);\n            color: var(--color-dark);\n        }\n        header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-primary);\n        }\n        header input {\n            padding: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            width: 70%;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;\n        }\n        header button {\n            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;\n            border: none;\n            background-color: var(--color-dark);\n            color: white;\n            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--color-red);\n            padding: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n        #promotion-banner {\n            background-color: var(--color-orange);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n        #promotion-banner span {\n            display: block;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        #product-gallery img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        #product-gallery div {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 0.5rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        #product-gallery div img {\n            width: 50px;\n            height: 50px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        #product-info h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--color-dark);\n        }\n        #pricing-section {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: baseline;\n            gap: 1rem;\n        }\n        #pricing-section span:first-child {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--color-red);\n        }\n        #pricing-section span:last-child {\n            text-decoration: line-through;\n            color: gray;\n        }\n        #pricing-section div {\n            margin-left: auto;\n            color: var(--color-orange);\n        }\n        #coupon-section ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        #coupon-section ul li {\n            background-color: var(--color-light);\n            padding: 0.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-orange);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        #purchase-channel {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 1rem;\n        }\n        #purchase-channel button {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        #purchase-channel button:first-child {\n            background-color: var(--color-orange);\n            color: white;\n        }\n        #purchase-channel button:last-child {\n            background-color: var(--color-red);\n            color: white;\n        }\n        #comment-section h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        #comment-section div {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        #comment-section ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        #comment-section ul li {\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n        #cart-modal {\n            display: none;\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            z-index: 1000;\n            width: 300px;\n        }\n        #cart-modal button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-red);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header id=\"search-bar\">\n        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"搜索商品...\">\n        <button>搜索</button>\n    </header>\n    <nav id=\"nav-bar\">\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">首页</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">分类</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">购物车</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n    <section id=\"promotion-banner\">\n        <div>春节特惠限时抢购</div>\n        <span>剩余时间：02:15:30</span>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"product-gallery\">\n        <img src=\"product-main.jpg\" alt=\"产品主图\">\n        <div>\n            <img src=\"thumb1.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图1\">\n            <img src=\"thumb2.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图2\">\n            <img src=\"thumb3.jpg\" alt=\"缩略图3\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"product-info\">\n        <h1>品牌名称 产品名称</h1>\n        <p>产地：中国 规格：500g 精选优质原料</p>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"pricing-section\">\n        <span>¥99</span>\n        <span>¥199</span>\n        <div>春节抢购倒计时：02:15:30</div>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"coupon-section\">\n        <ul>\n            <li>满100减20</li>\n            <li>满200减50</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>优惠券使用后，结算价格自动更新</p>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"purchase-channel\">\n        <button>加入购物车</button>\n        <button>立即购买</button>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"comment-section\">\n        <h2>用户评论</h2>\n        <div>\n            <label>筛选：</label>\n            <select>\n                <option>全部</option>\n                <option>好评</option>\n                <option>差评</option>\n            </select>\n        </div>\n        <ul>\n            <li>用户A：非常满意！</li>\n            <li>用户B：质量不错，发货快。</li>\n        </ul>\n    </section>\n    <div id=\"cart-modal\">\n        <h2>购物确认</h2>\n        <p>品牌名称 产品名称 500g</p>\n        <span>最终价格：¥99</span>\n        <button>确认支付</button>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
  ]
